response.name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
response.description: A compound exercise targeting the anterior/deltoids, with secondary engagement of traps and triceps. Performed seated or standing.

response.name: Lateral Raises
response.description: Targets medial deltoids for shoulder width. Raise weights laterally to shoulder height while maintaining slight elbow bend.

response.name: Barbell Upright Row
response.description: Works lateral and posterior deltoids, traps, and upper back. Lifts barbell vertically while keeping elbows high.

response.name: Face Pulls
response.description: Targets rear deltoids and rotator cuff muscles. Pulls rope attachment towards face with elbows wide.

response.name: Arnold Press
response.description: Combines shoulder press with rotational movement. Starts with palms inward, rotates hands upward during lift.
